com.interpss.dstab.devent

Interface SetPointChangeEvent

  • All Superinterfaces:
    BusDynamicEvent, com.hazelcast.nio.serialization.DataSerializable, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, NameTag, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    SetPointChangeEventImpl

    public interface SetPointChangeEvent
extends BusDynamicEvent
    A representation of the model object 'Set Point Change Event'. machine set point change bus synamic event

    The following features are supported:

    • Controller Type
    • Change Value
    • Abusolute Change
    • Mach Id
    See Also:
